erty_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Crowd-at-Sick-New-World-Festival-in-Las-Vegas-Nevada-2023.-CREDIT_-Greg-Doherty_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Crowd-at-Sick-New-World-Festival-in-Las-Vegas-Nevada-2023.-CREDIT_-Greg-Doherty_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Crowd-at-Sick-New-World-Festival-in-Las-Vegas-Nevada-2023.-CREDIT_-Greg-Doherty_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Crowd-at-Sick-New-World-Festival-in-Las-Vegas-Nevada-2023.-CREDIT_-Greg-Doherty_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Crowd-at-Sick-New-World-Festival-in-Las-Vegas-Nevada-2023.-CREDIT_-Greg-Doherty_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Crowd-at-Sick-New-World-Festival-in-Las-Vegas-Nevada-2023.-CREDIT_-Greg-Doherty_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Sick New World 音乐节在宣布阵容仅几周后就取消了计划于 2025 年举行的音乐节。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/metallica-amsterdam-live-review-2023-setlist-photos-m72-3436887">Metallica 阿姆斯特丹现场演出：仍然是最伟大的重金属乐队</a></strong></li></ul><p>该音乐节以摇滚、新金属和工业为主， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sick-new-world-festival-announces-2025-line-up-with-linkin-park-metallica-evanescence-qotsa-tickets-3803073">今年十月已是第三届了</a>。</p><p>此前定于 4 月 12 日在拉斯维加斯音乐节场地举行的音乐节已公布了超过 50 个名字，其中<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/linkin-park">Linkin Park</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/metallica">Metallica</a>将领衔主演，同时还有<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/evanescence">Evanence</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/queens-of-the-stone-age">Queens Of The Stone Age</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gojira">Gojira</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/afi">AFI 等乐队</a>的表演。</p><p>最初预定参加的乐队还有<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-flaming-lips">The Flaming Lips</a> 、the <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-sisters-of-mercy">Sisters Of Mercy</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/meshuggah">Meshuggah</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cradle-of-filth">Cradle Of Filth</a> 、X、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/refused">Refused</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cannibal-corpse">Cannibal Corpse</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lacuna-coil">Lacuna Coil</a> 。与此同时，路易斯安那州污泥金属制造商 Acid Bath <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sludge-metal-legends-acid-bath-to-reunite-after-28-years-for-sick-new-world-festival-3803481">将于 1997 年以来在音乐节上首次亮相</a>。</p><p>但现在，组织者宣布由于“不可预见的情况”取消该节日。</p><p>在昨天（11 月 29 日）分享给 Instagram 的一份声明中，电影节写道：“我们非常失望地宣布，《病态新世界》将不再于 2025 年 4 月 12 日在拉斯维加斯举行。尽管我们尽了最大努力，但我们”我们遇到了无法预见的情况，无法克服明年的展会。</p><p> “我们衷心感谢所有忠实的 SNW 粉丝，他们计划与我们一起参加另一场硬摇滚、哥特、另类和重音乐的文化庆典。请继续关注有关 Sick New World 的更多和未来信息。直接从 Front Gate Tickets 购买的门票将在短短 30 天内自动退款至原来的付款方式。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DC98nhtThqU/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><di